<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٢٣٤ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" إِذَا أَذِنَ لَهُ سَيِّدُهُ فِي الشِّرَاءِ، فَهُوَ ضَامِنٌ لِدَيْنِهِ،<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا لَمْ يَأْذَنْ لَهُ فَهُوَ فِي ذِمَّةِ الْعَبْدِ يَقُولُ:</span> لَا يُبَاعُ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٢٨٥⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٥٢٣٥ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ الثَّوْرِيُّ:</span> وَقَوْلُنَا: <span class="c2">«يُبَاعُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>